# Root-level safety net. Build-output folders (dist/, build/, .output/, etc.)
# are intentionally NOT ignored here: portafolio-portal/public/* contains the
# compiled demo builds, which must be tracked for the portfolio to work when
# deployed. Each source project has its own .gitignore scoping those rules
# correctly to its own root.

node_modules/
vendor/

.env
.env.local
.env.*.local
.env.backup
.env.production
!.env.example

*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*

.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

.idea/
*.suo
*.sw?
